title: Trend Asunder 7/24: Paw Patrol, Halloween Horror Nights, Dave Portnoy,  UFOs

description:
On this edition of Trend Asunder Jack and Miles discuss the rumor that Paw Patrol is getting cancelled, Halloween Horror Nights is actually cancelled and people are upset, Dave Portnoy of Barstool Sports interviewed Donald Trump and has caused in-fighting at Barstool, and the NY Times is releasing more stories about UFOs.
